		margin: 20px auto;
		background-color: #eee;
		border: #ccc 1px solid;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

		.rank-lists > li {
			width: 229px;
			float: left;
			border-right: #ccc 1px solid;
			overflow: hidden;
		}

	.rank-type {
		padding: 20px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

		.rank-type > img {
			float: left;
			width: 80px;
			height: 80px;
			margin-right: 10px;
		}

		.rank-type > a {
			font-size: 15px;
